user.bio:
I have 14 years experience working in the animation industry on film, television and game productions and am currently working in London at Axis Animation as a Lead Animator on various TV and VR projects.

My core skills include:

- 3D character, creature and facial animation (Cartoon or Realistic)
- Performance capture planning and direction
- Motion Editing
- Animation creation and setup within real-time engines for games and VR (CryEngine / UE4)
- Pre-visualization for film, television and advertising
- Character Rigging within Maya, 3ds Max and MotionBuilder
- Animation workshops and lectures

user.name: NOWAY VIDEO CLUB
user.bio: NOWAY Video Club is a NYC based animation studio. Founded in 2013 by SVA graduates Peyton Skyler (USA) and Celeste Lai (Taiwan). NOWAY Video Club was founded under the guiding principle that there is no one way to tell a story, but a story’s merit is dependent on it’s ability to transmit a meaningful message. NOWAY seeks to create videos of merit, for any audience, and strives for equal collaboration between each other, and between friends from around the world.

data.name: The Cat's Meow Cat Cafe
data.description:
The Cat's Meow plans to be the first cat cafe in Michigan, located in Ann Arbor Michigan. The Cat's Meow will be a cafe that is divided into two sections, part coffee shop as well as part cat rescue shelter. We have partnered with Happy Hearts Feline Rescue for the adoption process of the cats. We have also partnered with Mason Jar Coffee Co. out of Linden, MI as our specialty coffee roaster. We may also be bringing in baked goods. We plan to make downtown Ann Arbor our home.

http://igg.me/at/thecatsmeowcatcafe/x
